import sys,math

Prime_Nos=[]

def Gen_Primes() :
    for i in range(2,1032) :
        count=0
        for j in range(1,i) :
            if i%j==0 :
                pass
            else :
                count+=1
        if j==i-1 and count==i-2:
            Prime_Nos.append(i)                

def CheckIsPrime(number) :
    for i in Prime_Nos :
        if number%i==0 and number!=i :
            return False
    return True
